        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[女性有很多身份，每一个角色都不简单。深圳有这样一群女性，她们一身“武艺”，敢查“夺命黑诊所”；她们不惧危险，面对不健康不卫生，敢对不合格送上“封条”；...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[女性有很多身份，每一个角色都不简单。<br><br>深圳有这样一群女性，她们一身“武艺”，敢查“夺命黑诊所”；她们不惧危险，面对不健康不卫生，敢对不合格送上“封条”；她们还写得一手科普“好剧本”，让你更懂捍卫自己的健康……<br><br>今天是<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%89%E5%85%AB%E5%A6%87%E5%A5%B3%E8%8A%82%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#三八妇女节#</span></a> ，让卫带你认识那个她！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[送花花]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/cb/2022_Flowers_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E8%87%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E8%87%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳女性自有力量#</span></a>  👇🏻<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4876979791659022" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫生监督的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/ac97bb04gy1hbsairlokoj21tk10wb29.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/i7Rbw6WPgx083HIlmCUw01041200WCDK0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1678339332&amp;ssig=oKkRNncEW3&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/elPsFpP2gx083HIk3kRy01041200uHVa0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1678339332&amp;ssig=FakrnzHhDf&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/EgdOWsrRgx083HIjH9Lq01041200jHW80E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1678339332&amp;ssig=